Package: nearPointR
Title: Interactive Nearest Location Visualization Using Leaflet in R
Version: 0.0.0.01
Authors@R: 
    person("Prasad Madushanka Dauglas", "Dambure Liyanage", , "prasad.dream13@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The nearPointR package facilitates interactive visualization of nearest locations on a map using the Leaflet library in R. Also nearest location data can be downloaded as csv, json, kml file types.
